What is SDLC?
SDLC is shortform of Software Development Life cycle
SDLC is a standard practice to deliverying a quality product
SDLC is process that followed by industry to design, develop and test high quality product

Phases/Standards of SDLC:
    Planning & Requiring
    Defining/Documentation
    Designing[High level design & Low level design]
    Building 
    Testing
    Deploying

Building, Testing, Deploying are the main phases for DevOps engineer fastens the process by automating these phases.

e.g. Agile, Waterfall model ...